flowchart LR
    Dev[Desarrollador]
    PR[Pull Request a main]
    Push[Push a main]
    Tag[Tag v X Y Z]

    subgraph CI["W1 - Workflow CI"]
        Compile[mvn compile o npm ci]
        Tests[mvn test o vitest]
        Lint[Checkstyle o ESLint]
        Coverage[JaCoCo umbral 75 porciento]
        GodFiles[Top 10 archivos largos]
    end

    subgraph Release["W2 - Workflow Release"]
        Build[Docker build multistage]
        Push2[Push a ghcr.io]
        Tags[Tags semver - latest]
        OpenAPI[Publicar openapi.json en GitHub Release]
    end

    Sync[repository_dispatch<br/>backend dispara regen tipos en frontend]

    Dev --> PR
    Dev --> Push
    Dev --> Tag

    PR --> CI
    Push --> CI

    Tag --> Release
    Release --> Sync

    CI -->|verde| MergeOk[Merge permitido]
    CI -->|rojo| Block[Bloquea merge]

    classDef ok fill:#16a34a,stroke:#15803d,color:#f0fdf4
    classDef bad fill:#dc2626,stroke:#b91c1c,color:#fef2f2
    class MergeOk ok
    class Block bad
